134
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,760
Ioan.

135
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,840
Ioan!

136
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:42,840
-Preciso falar com você. 
-O que foi?

137
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:45,200
