223
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,840
Como profissional?

224
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:10,000
Sim. Ela vai adorar.

225
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,400
Oi, dorminhoco.

226
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,400
Caramba.

227
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:24,640
